WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.181 --> 00:00:12.551
 I drew four hours of this painting. 

00:00:17.241 --> 00:00:22.371
 (The meaning of this painting) is that the boss of the tiger is brought to justice. 

00:00:44.948 --> 00:00:56.201
 It’s a little weird because I want to paint this boss. 

00:00:58.616 --> 00:01:08.608
 Also feel a little uncomfortable 

00:01:12.997 --> 00:01:24.716
 Because he used to be this thing for my boss, I feel a bit contradictory. 

00:01:39.104 --> 00:01:47.677
 I will not teach him before (the boss) will teach me 

00:01:46.774 --> 00:01:51.604
 I think he (in the beginning) is a pretty person. 

00:01:52.225 --> 00:02:09.504
 But after working, I found that when I did something wrong, he would be very excited. 

00:02:10.196 --> 00:02:15.715
 Will be simple 

00:02:29.311 --> 00:02:52.026
 He (the boss) must be punished for this matter 

00:03:16.845 --> 00:03:19.871
 Because I don't want this to affect other people. 

00:03:20.482 --> 00:03:28.455
 Because it is a very independent thing 

00:03:28.635 --> 00:03:37.412
 So don’t want to be involved in people who are not related to the event. 

00:03:37.860 --> 00:03:42.665
 I think his (supervisor) family is irrelevant to this matter. 

00:03:42.927 --> 00:03:47.150
 I feel very uncomfortable if this matter is openly inconvenient for them (the family of the boss). 

00:03:59.531 --> 00:04:09.497
 Because this is the first time in Singapore. 

00:04:09.736 --> 00:04:20.751
 Also because (the boss) has passed the legal control 

00:04:23.188 --> 00:04:25.294
 Means that this happened 

00:04:48.075 --> 00:05:00.958
 Also, because I only got a salary of 500 yuan a month, which is lower than any job. No one knows that I am embarrassed. 

00:05:20.767 --> 00:05:33.485
 Because my parents know that I was an intern before. 

00:05:34.065 --> 00:06:03.707
 My mother asked me in 2011. I told her boss that my salary is so low because my graduate school is not ideal. 

00:06:05.556 --> 00:06:22.653
 My mother also advised me to go to other jobs because the monthly salary of 500 yuan is too small, but I am hesitating. 

